{"tid":2372819,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"拜登準國務卿支持特朗普強硬對華立場 「願見美國收容出走港人」","createTime":"2021-01-20T04:11:04.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-20T05:21:03.000Z","uid":239336,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"83a6cc09ee790498df1186b94172f77d0b2a66c5","tid":2372819,"uid":239336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T04:11:04.000Z","msg":"美國參議院周二就拜登提名的多位內閣人選召開提名確認聽證會，對華立場成為議員關注焦點，議員向準國務卿布林肯（Antony Blinken）問及香港問題。<br />\n<br />\n參議院外委會就國務卿人選舉行提名確認聽證會，議員關切美中關係及北京對香港、台灣的侵略野心。共和黨籍參議院外委會主席里施（James Risch）開場致詞就向布林肯提及中國挑戰與台灣的重要性。里施表示，中國是美國戰略與全球競爭者，中共經常進行經濟脅迫、軍事侵略、人權侵犯與影響力作戰，他預期拜登政府將尋求兩黨合作，共同面對中共帶來的挑戰，而其中一項挑戰就是台灣。里施指出，北京摧毀香港自治，使台灣未來的問題更加逼切與嚴肅。中國軍事現代化及擴張作為大幅度改變印太區域權力平衡，讓美國軍隊與印太盟友夥伴都處於危險之中。他說：「台灣是重要戰略議題之一，應持續被視為（美國）戰略要務。」<br />\n<br />\n共和黨參議員羅姆尼（Mitt Romney）則指出，中國顯然想成為全球地緣政治、經濟與軍事領袖，並將威權主義強加在他國身上，這可能對世界各地人民自由造成巨大威脅，問布林肯對台灣與美國對台承諾的想法為何。<br />\n布林肯表示，對即將卸任的總統特朗普的強硬對華立場表示支持。布林肯表示，北京無疑是美國最大挑戰，美中關係對抗成份增加，有競爭但也有合作面向。他說：美國應開始從一個有力位置與中國打交道，而非弱勢位置。他說，當美國與盟友合作，而非不當批評他們時；當美國參與、領導國際組織，而非退出讓中國制訂規則時；當人權遭侵犯或香港民主遭踐踏，美國起身維護自身價值時，「這些時刻都能讓美國取得有力位置」。<br />\n<br />\n布林肯表示，希望看到美國收容由香港逃亡過來的人。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20210120/75MGIBMISBGTFFWGDS4FLF52J4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210120%2F75MGIBMISBGTFFWGDS4FLF52J4%2F&d=CthjHxCXz%2Bl0vOF3eBkmesljX8qB7Opg6os1DAz3scM%3D&h=07b75578\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210120%2F75MGIBMISBGTFFWGDS4FLF52J4%2F&h=30567eca\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20210120/75MGIBMISBGTFFWGDS4FLF52J4/</a>"},{"pid":"89b993c2319891d671bd5215fb3f557188492781","tid":2372819,"uid":333199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T04:11:49.000Z","msg":"TRUMP TRUMP<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dabec7c06a271b88fa1c6181a911ff8774efda9d","tid":2372819,"uid":239336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T04:13:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c54e3575e6377b566b3a2e58355e47a1efa19435","tid":2372819,"uid":191926,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T04:14:21.000Z","msg":"即係英國咁<br />\n點都要揹人權債 (應付國內外壓力)<br />\n<br />\n如其搞制裁，貿易戰<br />\n不如收人<br />\n<br />\n好像默克爾咁"},{"pid":"54d948231edb222fdd0ddd5187b1e6b96e293c25","tid":2372819,"uid":110832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T04:14:27.000Z","msg":"下話"},{"pid":"a149e2f7a8c87a7185473ed7b4f84fe90d1e571f","tid":2372819,"uid":239336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T04:40:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e648b42f551987c7d3bad16e9be4b39a431fe6f","tid":2372819,"uid":70301,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T04:50:00.000Z","msg":"拜燈團隊，聽住先<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8cc6dfab7ed31cc828d496d556a74e052bdb15e1","tid":2372819,"uid":58841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T05:17:39.000Z","msg":"口頭支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/ok.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca5e0a915b3c52221126d9a81315b5232a98d5ef","tid":2372819,"uid":328494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedB